he_Wad" title="Joan the Wad">Joan the Wad</a></i>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Psotnik" title="Psotnik">Psotnik</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/P%C3%BAca" title="Púca">Púca</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Puck_(mythology)" title="Puck (mythology)">Puck</a>/<a href="/wiki/Robin_Goodfellow" title="Robin Goodfellow" class="mw-redirect">Robin Goodfellow</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Radande" title="Radande">Radande</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Redcap" title="Redcap">Redcap</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Rusalka" title="Rusalka">Rusalka</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/S%C3%A2nzian%C4%83" title="Sânziană">Sânziană</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Selkie" title="Selkie">Selkie</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sprite_(creature)" title="Sprite (creature)">Sprite</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sylph" title="Sylph">Sylph</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tomte" title="Tomte">Tomte</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Troll" title="Troll">Troll</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Vila_(fairy)#Vila" title="Vila (fairy)" class="mw-redirect">Vila</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Vodyanoy" title="Vodyanoy">Vodyanoy</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Water_sprite" title="Water sprite">Water sprite</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Wight" title="Wight">Wight</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Xana" title="Xana">Xan